title: SEC Delays Decision On Hashdex And Grayscale ETF Applications
description: The United States Securities and Exchange Commission has delayed its decision on the Hashdex spot bitcoin ETF application and Grayscale’s Ether futures filing. The agency stated in its filing that it would make a decision on the applications by the 1st of January, 2024.
